Subject: [DSECRG-09-068] SAP NetWaver SLD -  multiple XSS


Digital Security Research Group [DSecRG] Advisory  DSecRG-09-068

Application:                    SAP NetWeaver SLD
Versions Affected:              6.4 - 7.02
Vendor URL:                     http://SAP.com
